sentences: See film on juba liiga kaua kestnud - lõpetage see nüüd! Või te ei tea neid tähti? Enama neist filmides pole näha.
Ta ei saa enam tunda, et tal on vigu.
context: 'Enam' is used to express that something has increased beyond a previous level or continued for an extended period. It often implies excessiveness or reaching a limit in contexts like time, quantity, or repetition.
